TITLE: Building Ubuntu Kernel for Syscall Extraction
DESCRIPTION: Commands for cloning, configuring and building the Ubuntu kernel source to prepare it for syscall prototype extraction. The build generates necessary unistd header files even if full compilation fails.
SOURCE: https://github.com/panda-re/panda-ng/blob/main/plugins/syscalls2/MAINTENANCE.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
git clone git://kernel.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ubuntu-bionic.git
cd ubuntu-bionic
git checkout Ubuntu-4.15.0-97.98
cat ./debian.master/config/{config.common.ubuntu,i386/config.common.i386,i386/config.flavour.generic} > .config
make
```

